
Latest release: @RELEASE_VERSION@
http://geodesystems.com/repository/alias/release

repository.war: self contained war file for running under Tomcat, Glassfish, etc

ramaddaserver.zip: stand-alone version of RAMADDA. Just needs Java to run. Download and unzip the file

ramaddainstaller.zip: contains script to setup a Linux box with postgres and ramadda

There are 4 sets of bundled plugins:
coreplugins.jar
bioplugins.jar
geoplugins.jar
miscplugins.jar

These plugins can get installed during the initial system install and will get automatically updated.
You can download and install the plugins after the fact. Just copy them into your RAMADDA home/plugins 
directory.

The plugins directory contains all of the individual plugins






